title: Divisional Round Picks Against the Spread, Best Bets, Gambling Advice (Football 1/10)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Pete Prisco and R.J. White for gambling advice for the divisional round of the NFL playoffs. The guys discuss Vikings-49ers (7:45), Titans-Ravens (15:20), Texans-Chiefs (26:00) and Seahawks-Packers (33:30).
